  "prompt": "What is the process to get a job at Wipro?",
  "response": "Here's the typical process to get a job at Wipro:\n\n1. Application Stage\n- Visit Wipro's official careers website\n- Create a profile\n- Search for suitable job openings\n- Submit your resume/application online\n- Match job requirements with your qualifications\n\n2. Initial Screening\n- HR reviews your application\n- Checks educational background\n- Verifies resume details\n- Matches candidate profile with job requirements\n\n3. Online Assessment\n- Aptitude test\n- Technical skills assessment\n- Logical reasoning test\n- Programming/coding challenges (for technical roles)\n\n4. Interview Rounds\n- Initial telephonic/video screening interview\n- Technical interview\n- HR interview\n- Managerial interview\n- Sometimes multiple interview rounds\n\n5. Selection Process\n- Performance evaluation in all interview stages\n- Background verification\n- Reference checks\n- Final job offer\n\nAdditional Tips:\n- Keep resume updated\n- Highlight relevant skills\n- Prepare for technical and HR interviews\n- Practice coding/aptitude tests\n- Demonstrate knowledge of Wipro's business\n- Show communication and problem-solving skills\n\nRecommended Preparation:\n- Strong academic background\n- Relevant technical/domain skills\n- Good communication abilities\n- Understanding of current industry trends",
